//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brian-mcbride-stars-of-the-lid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brian-mcbride-stars-of-the-lid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brian-mcbride-stars-of-the-lid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>著名环境项目 Stars Of The Lid 的成员 Brian McBride 去世，享年 53 岁。</p><p>他的乐队成员 Adam Wiltzie 在 Instagram 上透露了这一消息。没有给出死因。</p><p>威尔茨写道：“我非常悲伤地告诉大家布莱恩·麦克布莱德去世了。” “我爱这个人，我们会想念他的。”</p><p> McBride 和 Wiltzie 于 1993 年在德克萨斯州奥斯汀组建了 Stars Of The Lid，乐队名称意为“位于您的眼睛和眼睑之间的您自己的个人影院”。</p><p>两人发行了六张录音室专辑，从 1995 年的首张专辑《Music For Nitrous Oxide》到 2007 年的《And Their Refinement Of The Decline》。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwdDLnWtCO-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000