阿洛·帕克斯 (Arlo Parks) 讲述她与雷丁·霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Reading Holly Humberstone) 合作的惊喜以及对北极猴子的热爱https://www.nme.com/news/music/arlo-parks-reading-and-leeds-2023-interview-3489439?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=arlo-parks-reading-and-leeds-2023-interviewLiberty Dunworth Sun, 27 Aug 2023 18:10:55 +0000 FestivalsMusic InterviewsMusic NewsNewsReading & Leeds FestivalIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3489439 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在雷丁和利兹演出结束后，这位歌手与亨伯斯通一起惊喜表演了“客房服务”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/arlo-parks-reading-and-leeds-2023-interview-3489439">阿洛·帕克斯 (Arlo Parks) 发表了一篇关于她与 Reading Holly Humberstone 合作的惊喜以及对 Arctic Monkeys 的热爱的文章，该文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2023">Reading &amp; Leeds 2023 的</a>后台采访了<em>NME</em> ，讨论了她即将出版的诗集、与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a>的惊喜亮相，以及她对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a>首张专辑的喜爱。查看上面的完整采访。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/reading-festival-2023-liveblog-all-of-the-weekends-action-as-it-happens-3488589">2023 年读书节直播博客：周末发生的所有活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手、词曲作者兼诗人于昨天下午（8 月 26 日）以她新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/arlo-parks-my-soft-machine-review-a-subtle-step-forward-3448016">《My Soft Machine》</a>中的两首歌曲拉开了她的演出序幕，早在独立巨头<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>登台以他们的表演结束当晚之前。标题集。令歌迷惊讶的是，她还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-arlo-parks-join-holly-humberstone-for-a-duet-at-reading-festival-2023-3488941">霍莉·亨伯斯通主舞台表演期间短暂出现在舞台上</a>，与她一起表演她的新单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-announces-debut-album-paint-my-bedroom-black-3462992">“Room Service”</a> 。</p><p>随后在后台与<em>NME</em>会面时，帕克斯谈到了客串的出现，并回忆了亨伯斯通即将发行的首张专辑中的新单曲对她的特殊意义。</p><p> “说实话，她是最可爱的。我们见过几次面，我是她音乐的忠实粉丝，”她开始说道。 “然后她在最后一刻问我是否想和她一起上台。</p><p> “这是我非常喜欢做的事情，”她补充道，接着回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/phoebe-bridgers-live-at-glastonbury-2022-review-setlist-photos-3255459">去年她与菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers) 的亮相</a>。 “我在 Glastonbury 与 Phoebe 和 Coachella 乐队一起表演过……我认为登上舞台确实有一些特别之处<br />与朋友。” </p><figure id="attachment_3489448" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3489448" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3489448" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270.jpg" alt="阿洛帕克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-3@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3489448" class="wp-caption-text">阿洛·帕克斯。图片来源：莎拉·路易丝·贝内特</figcaption></figure><p>“‘客房服务’是一首多么美妙的歌曲，你知道吗？那种想念远方朋友的感觉，想要把自己锁在远离世界的地方，重新建立联系，深入研究你们的友谊。所以这也是一首特别的歌曲。”</p><p>在与<em>NME</em>的讨论中，帕克斯还谈到了她即将出版的诗集<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/arlo-parks-poetry-book-the-magic-border-fragments-from-my-soft-machine-jai-paul-jasmine-3455349"><em>《神奇边界：来自我的软机器的诗歌和片段》</em></a> ，并回顾了她发现自己最喜欢歌词的艺术家，即 Arctic Monkeys 2006 年的首张专辑《Whatever People Say》我是，那不是我”。</p><p> “[有]这么多，”她告诉<em>NME</em> 。 “我是独立乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-thief">Big Thief</a>的忠实粉丝，我经常喜欢 Adrian LANKA 的歌词，因为它们是如此丰富、富有诗意和美丽。</p><p> “我年轻时经常这样做，因为我是摇滚音乐的忠实粉丝，”她继续说道。 “因此，[有]很多<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a>和 Arctic Monkeys ——他们的第一张唱片是我在 iPod Nano 上购买的第一张唱片……我着迷地阅读了该唱片的所有歌词。我喜欢那张专辑”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3489449" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3489449" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3489449" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="阿洛·帕克斯。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Arlo-Parks-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3489449" class="wp-caption-text">阿洛·帕克斯。图片来源：莎拉·路易丝·贝内特</figcaption></figure><p>在聊天即将结束时，这位 23 岁的音乐家还回顾了<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/arlo-parks-cover-interview-2020-black-dog-eugene-2714222">她之前在<em>NME</em>接受的采访</a>——在她的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/arlo-parks-collapsed-in-sunbeams-review-2865149">《Collapsed In Sunbeams》</a>发行后不久，她承认她觉得这“很奇怪”接受她在全球各地聚集粉丝的事实。</p><p> “我认为这不可能是正常的，你知道，”她昨天回答道，并被问到两年后她的立场是否发生了变化。</p><p> “我认为很多人一生都在卧室或工作室里创作音乐，但它永远不会超出他们的友谊群体。 [因此]能够在东京卖掉一个房间，让人们喜欢唱歌，即使这甚至不是他们的母语，这永远是我认为我永远不会认为理所当然的事情。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2023">请返回<em>NME</em> ，</a>了解 Reading &amp; Leeds 2023 的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/arlo-parks-reading-and-leeds-2023-interview-3489439">阿洛·帕克斯 (Arlo Parks) 发表了一篇关于她与 Reading Holly Humberstone 合作的惊喜以及对 Arctic Monkeys 的热爱的文章，该文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
